 Recording artiste Paul Okoye aka Rudeboy has spoken about what he does when eating chicken. Explaining his eating habit, the Okoye twin explained that he throws caution to the wind when eating chicken especially when it has to do with the bones. The “Reason with Me” singer appealed to persons who may happen to him crushing chicken bones in public to resist the urge to judge him. Read Also: [PHOTO]: Rude Boy Of Estranged P-Square, Flaunts His Crib And Cars On Instagram